*                                  DT_INSUL.SIZ
*
*
*   
* List of available wall and roof insulation.
*
*Each item in the insulation file must be unique from the other entries, except that 
*there can be a starter roll to give the same insulation twice with the first item being 
*the starter and the second item being used a the interior locations. 
*Each item is classified by the Type and Thickness. There cannot be multiple Types of 
*the same thickness, except for the starter roll scenario. 
*
*                                                        --Wall--   --Roof---
*Type   Description               Part      Width  Thick Top  Bot   Eave Peak Lap  Length  Weight
*                                 Name       (mm)   (mm) (mm) (mm)  (mm) (mm) (mm)  (mm)  (kg/m2)
*----- ----------------------   ----------  ------ ----- ---- ----  ---- ---- ---- ------ -------
