 'GW'  'GlassWool 50 NoFoil '   'GW50    '   1200    50     0    0  150   150  0   15000.  1.20
 'GW'  'GlassWool 75 W/Foil '   'GW75 F  '   1200    75     0    0  150   150  0    8000.  1.20
 'GW'  'GlassWool 50 Local  '   'GW50 LM '   1200    50     0    0  150   150  0   15000.  1.20
